{"tid":2510573,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【印度偏方】迷信牛尿牛糞可消毒防疫　印度政客強餵重症患者飲牛尿治病","createTime":"2021-04-30T09:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T09:23:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"05cec68ec07185eec8e85ee0f5a819d42dfbe570","tid":2510573,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"印度新冠肺炎疫情大爆發，再多近38萬人染疫，全國累計確診人數超過1800萬，超過20萬人死亡。疫情失控、醫療系統崩潰之時，執政黨印度人民黨（BJP）的黨員竟在Twitter上傳一條給新冠患者飲牛尿的影片，引起當地民眾撻伐。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，影片是由印度總理莫迪（Narendra Damodardas Modi）所屬政黨──印度人民黨蘇拉特分部祕書長賓達爾（Kishor Bindal）上傳至Twitter，並寫著：「成員正在幫助新冠肺炎病人」。<br />\n<br />\n從短片可見，一名年長的新冠重症患者正躺在病床上，嘴還插著喉管，仰賴呼吸機生存。但病床旁邊一名BJP黨員，竟將手中一瓶黃色液體，倒入患者口中。而患者完全無法拒絕或呼救，只能眼睜睜地看著對方將牛尿倒入自己口中。<br />\n<br />\n據拍攝影片者介紹，這名患者喝的就是「Gau Mutra」（牛尿）。<br />\n影片隨即在網上瘋傳，大批網民怒斥行為荒謬：<br />\n其後，Kishor Bindal立刻將影片刪除，暫時沒有對事件作任何解釋。<br />\n<br />\n議員：牛尿、牛糞有助治療冠狀病毒<br />\n其實早於去年，印度人民黨議員Suman Haripriya就曾在集會上表示，牛尿、牛糞有助治療冠狀病毒，甚至癌症。另一名人民黨議員Sanjay Gupta也稱，古印度教儀式及牛尿可殺死空氣中及體內的病毒；用牛糞清掃地板也可遏制病毒。<br />\n&quot;古老的印度人都會用牛糞清掃地板，已證實這是種消毒劑，只不過現今的人類忘記了。我肯定如果大家再次這樣做，病毒就不會入侵他們的家。另外，大家也應該飲牛尿來預防病毒，因為母牛（Gau Mata）的產物都有神奇抗病毒的特性。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n當中更有印度男子身體力行，以牛糞沐浴的影片，震驚無數網民。影片中，4名男子站在牛糞池中，表示「牛糞是靈丹妙藥，如果我們每6個月用牛糞洗一次澡，就可以潔淨全身。」然後全身浸在牛糞池中。又有印度男子直接在牛隻排尿期間，直接用新鮮牛尿洗面、飲尿。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2945787/urine_thumb_20210430_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2945787%2Furine_thumb_20210430_J_1024.jpg&h=e812aa4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8fb3f8e10b50891d19a8be8a069ef689fb798cb","tid":2510573,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好玩唔玩 玩屎"},{"pid":"6fc7c0cf290a9dbbd2acb91013953edd3f7f097d","tid":2510573,"uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e8fb3f8e10b50891d19a8be8a069ef689fb798cb","tid":2510573,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好玩唔玩 玩屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmemi1ZGJDt9D3ypyuGZuTsTu8Ca17bAF5S5bd8ms5SZYE?filename=UcnNsyv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUcnNsyv.png&h=56aef15b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36515791c3251081d9e9ac68833f81e9b54b989d","tid":2510573,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"有咩慘過中武肺？<br />\n就係中完仲要飲尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d315013c5fe6eb76fa851c4d21dd2821cb1efd68","tid":2510573,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:13:49.000Z","msg":"以毒攻毒<br />\n之那武肺<br />\n奇毒無比"},{"pid":"c92dcfd87a73e38197ed6900e24db4d5212c95bd","tid":2510573,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"真牛屎佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b41a72bd08b1ed0686cb6bb5e85d2e45fa13bc","tid":2510573,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:15:49.000Z","msg":"馬尿可以整咳水<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ddca5bac0fcabb5b2f1b100769689c606f0ffe","tid":2510573,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47b41a72bd08b1ed0686cb6bb5e85d2e45fa13bc","tid":2510573,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislik